{"tid":1592641,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"順天手足幫手留意下 打蘋果記者嗰幾個去咗順天","createTime":"2019-09-24T16:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T01:18:51.000Z","uid":226858,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0a4eebdc510ff62acb9995918e35537f687bb175","tid":1592641,"uid":226858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:56:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://streamable.com/f4pos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Ff4pos&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=403c19e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/f4pos</a><br />\n<br />\n一個黃盔白袖<br />\n一個黃盔黑袖<br />\n一個無盔灰面巾<br />\n打蘋果記者嗰幾條友同呢條片嘅match<br />\n條片喺順天影到"},{"pid":"5d726796dfebe8978a1a8dab93f9c12e35f80a0c","tid":1592641,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"abe00cccaa1dcb9b73b8048107fcd0619d1ebc6f","tid":1592641,"uid":146092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:58:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">HK Assembly Logo投票Link：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=6b0c0287\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vyTs8Wx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvyTs8Wx.jpg&h=306d0b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;關於Logo投票&gt;</span></span><br />\nHK Assembly成立的目的，不單是讓全港市民議論政事，更希望建立民主平台，讓全民以公投方式發聲，同時將平台民主制度完善，成為能與政制競爭的類政制。<br />\n但是在達到理想前，必須逐步累積技術和經驗。因此，我們決定對投票機制進行第一次測試，以現階段盡量民主的方式讓大家選出共同的「香港全民議政會」Logo。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;投票機制&gt;</span></span><br />\n投票採用兩輪的簡單多數制。最高票數的兩款將交由設計師作最後加工，在第二輛投票獲較高票數的一款將成為 HK Assembly 的官方 Logo。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">規則：</span></span><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: violet;\">一人一票</span> [1] <br />\n2. 第一輪投票時間：<span style=\"color: violet;\">24/9 11PM - 26/9 11PM</span> （香港時間，共48小時）[2]<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: violet;\">以「香港全民議政會」投票及發佈Channel投票：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=6b0c0287\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a> [3]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">投票需要你：</span></span><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: violet;\">加入Channel：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=6b0c0287\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n2. <span style=\"color: violet;\">投票</span><br />\n3. <span style=\"color: violet;\">叫朋友</span>加入Channel一起投票！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&lt;感謝支持&gt;</span></span><br />\n集合全港多名設計精英，文宣組共設計了七款 Logo，在此先向這些有心人<span style=\"color: violet;\">致謝</span>。<br />\n希望藉著這次投票，和大家一起開始建立<span style=\"color: violet;\">真正屬於香港人的民主議政平台</span>。<br />\n隨人數增加、平台民主及身份認證制度變得完善，希望HK Assembly將變得更具公信力，讓大家<span style=\"color: violet;\">投票救港</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">HK Assembly Logo投票Link：</span> <a href=\"https://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=6b0c0287\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n- - - - - - - - - -<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">隨意門：《香港全民議政會》 HK Assembly 正式成立 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1590386/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1590386/page/1</a><br />\n- - - - - - - - - -<br />\n[1] 暫時未有機制解決Telegram上一人多號引致一人多票的身份認證問題，但：<br />\n1. 這是初期階段未能解決的複雜問題<br />\n2. 估計一人多號佔使用者比例不高<br />\n3. 因為抵消效果，減少對投票結果影響<br />\n4. 對此投票問題，控制投票結果的誘因不大<br />\n[2] 兩款設計交由設計師作最後加工後，第二輛投票預計於29/9進行<br />\n[3]<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 無Telegram？【趁而家快D裝啦！】</span></span>隨人數增加、平台民主及身份認證制度變得完善，希望HK Assembly將變得更具公信力，讓大家投票救港！"},{"pid":"6fb5588817ceec66b8d9f64c3281059f2e69f887","tid":1592641,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:59:40.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">927新屋嶺 928民陣集會 929全球抗共 930三罷 10.1國殤遊行</span>"},{"pid":"cd5cf01578063bdadf13457684ee170f7d4593c8","tid":1592641,"uid":285776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:02:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2799ed076f4d80445ef70d4d53e918021f28744a","tid":1592641,"uid":322947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:03:09.000Z","msg":"p 牌照推"},{"pid":"5cb162f67a3b658933014c3d828189e3350b95bd","tid":1592641,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:03:17.000Z","msg":"GO"},{"pid":"1c8a871cd967c687228b65daba862a9b90276407","tid":1592641,"uid":318065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:03:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"005d58406c3366d672816750416d6f143450fb32","tid":1592641,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:07:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a605b364cf4cbf84c4e7f86431c8def2e6f6337a","tid":1592641,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:16:18.000Z","msg":"《行動》928 雨傘5週年 集會 yellow object<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590313</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"